description: The number of people to die with the virus on the island has risen to 18, the health minister confirms.
title: Coronavirus: Isle of Man death toll rises to 18 after two more deaths
title_page: Coronavirus: Isle of Man death toll rises to 18 after two more deaths - BBC News
maintext: He said: "We must all redouble our efforts and continue to fight against this disease to ensure as few families as possible lose their loved ones in this horrendous way."
